Tau is a micro-blogging service.

## installation

Run the following commands:

    git clone git://github.com/thinxer/tau.git
    cd tau
    git submodule init
    git submodule update
    mv conf_example.py conf.py
    vim conf.py

Depends on: python 2.6+, PIL, pymongo, webassets, pyyaml, cssmin.

    pip install pil pymongo webassets pyyaml cssmin
